{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2020-05-13-promise_combinators/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"박준우 블로그"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"af1f16bc-8ab6-548c-9073-b203196e2523","excerpt":"ES2020에  가 소개되었습니다. 여기에 더해 아직 TC39 Proposal Stage 3단계{:target=”_blank”}인  도 같이 공부하며, 정리해보려고 합니다. 프로미스 기본 개념 프로미스 상태 대기(pending): 이행(fulfilled)되거나 거부(rejected…","html":"<p>ES2020에 <code class=\"language-text\">Promise.allSettled</code> 가 소개되었습니다.</p>\n<p>여기에 더해 아직 <a href=\"https://github.com/tc39/proposals\">TC39 Proposal Stage 3단계</a>{:target=”_blank”}인 <code class=\"language-text\">Promise.any</code> 도 같이 공부하며, 정리해보려고 합니다.</p>\n<br>\n<h2>프로미스 기본 개념</h2>\n<br>\n<h3>프로미스 상태</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>대기(pending): 이행(fulfilled)되거나 거부(rejected)되지 않은 초기 상태를 뜻합니다.</li>\n<li>이행(fulfilled): 성공적으로 완료된 상태입니다.</li>\n<li>거부(rejected): 실패한 상태입니다.</li>\n<li>\n<p>처리(settled): 대기중이지 않으며 이행되거나 거부되었을때 처리되었다고 말합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">settled === !pending &amp;&amp; (fulfilled || rejected)</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<h3>Promise 프로토타입</h3>\n<p>3가지 메서드가 있습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\"><span class=\"token function\">fetch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"https://api.github.com/users\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>data <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token builtin\">console</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"data : \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> data<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">catch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token builtin\">console</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">error</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"error : \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> error<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">finally</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token builtin\">console</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Finally..!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<hr>\n<h2>Promise Combinators</h2>\n<br>\n<h3>4가지 Combinators</h3>\n<p>ES2015에서 소개된 <code class=\"language-text\">Promise.all</code> 과 <code class=\"language-text\">Promise.race</code> ,</p>\n<p>이번에 ES2020에서 소개된 <code class=\"language-text\">Promise.allSettled</code> ,</p>\n<p>그리고 마지막으로 곧 새로운 기능으로 합류될 예정인 <code class=\"language-text\">Promise.any</code> 가 있습니다.</p>\n<br>\n<h4>Promise.all</h4>\n<p>모든 프로미스가 이행(fullfilled)되거나, 하나라도 거부(rejected)되었을 때 프로미스 객체를 반환합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> promises <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">fetch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/api/a\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token string\">\"a\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">fetch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/api/b\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token string\">\"b\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">fetch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/api/c\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token string\">\"c\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">try</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> apiResponses <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">Promise</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">all</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>promises<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// 모든 프로미스가 fullfilled되면..</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">renderNewData</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>apiResponses<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">catch</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">displayError</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>reason<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<h4>Promise.race</h4>\n<p>가장 먼저 처리(settled)된 프로미스를 잡아내고 싶을 때 사용합니다.</p>\n<p>메소드이름처럼 정말 경주를 하는 것 같습니다.</p>\n<p>예시1)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> promises <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token function\">performVeryHeavyLogic</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token function\">rejectByForceAfterTimeoutMs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">5000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">try</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> result <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">Promise</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">race</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>promises<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// performVeryHeavyLogic()이 완료되면,</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">renderResult</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">catch</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">//rejectByForceAfterTimeoutMs()로 인해 5s 이상 지나거나 에러가 발생하면,</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">renderError</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>예시2)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\"><span class=\"token builtin\">Promise</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">race</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">fetch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"https://api.github.com/users/schacon\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>data <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> data<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">json</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">fetch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"https://api.github.com/users/pjhyett\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>data <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> data<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">json</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>data <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token builtin\">console</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">가 먼저 도착했어요!</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">catch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token builtin\">console</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">error</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"error : \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> error<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<h4>Promise.allSettled</h4>\n<p>모든 프로미스가 처리(settled)된 경우, 즉 모든 프로미스가 이행(fullfilled)되거나 거부(rejected)되었을 때 프로미스 객체를 반환합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> promises <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">fetch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/api/a\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token string\">\"a\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">fetch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/api/b\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token string\">\"b\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">fetch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/api/c\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token string\">\"c\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 일부는 이행(fullfilled)되고 일부는 거부(rejected)되었더라도</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">Promise</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">allSettled</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>promises<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// allSettled는 오직 처리(settled)되었는지만 확인합니다.</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">removeLoadingIndicator</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<h4>Promise.any</h4>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Promise.any</code> 는 <a href=\"https://github.com/tc39/proposal-promise-any\">TC39 Candidate stage (Stage 3)</a>{:target=”_blank”} 단계의 메소드입니다.</p>\n<p>여러 프로미스 중, 단 하나의 프로미스가 이행(fullfilled)되면 프로미스 객체를 반환합니다.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Promise.race</code> 는 이행(fullfilled)이나 거부(rejected)를 가리지않지만, <code class=\"language-text\">Promise.any</code> 는 이행(fullfilled)만을 취급합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> promises <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">fetch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/api/a\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token string\">\"a\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">fetch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/api/b\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token string\">\"b\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">fetch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/api/c\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token string\">\"c\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">try</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> first <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">Promise</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">any</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>promises<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// 가장 먼저 이행(fullfilled)된 프로미스</span>\n  <span class=\"token builtin\">console</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>first<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// ex: 'c'</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">catch</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// 모든 프로미스들이 거부(rejected)되어야지만,</span>\n  <span class=\"token builtin\">console</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">error</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<h3>Reference</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\">https://developer.mozilla.org/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise</a>{:target=”_blank”}</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pawelgrzybek.com/promise-combinators-explained/\">https://pawelgrzybek.com/promise-combinators-explained/</a>{:target=”_blank”}</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://v8.dev/features/promise-combinators\">https://v8.dev/features/promise-combinators</a>{:target=”_blank”}</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Promise Combinators 정리","date":"May 13, 2020","description":"ES2020에 Promise.allSettled이 소개되었습니다."}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020-05-12-map/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"ES6 Map"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020-07-28-chrome_devtools/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"<번역>시니어 프론트엔드 개발자처럼 크롬 개발자도구 사용하기"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"af1f16bc-8ab6-548c-9073-b203196e2523","previousPostId":"41a1f218-a888-554c-9d59-4e219752dd50","nextPostId":"1589cdb6-c5b0-5888-99b7-674f01be0775"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","916993862"]}